	* elf64-ppc.c, * elf64-s390.c, * elflink.c, * elfnn-aarch64.c,
	* elfnn-riscv.c, * elfxx-sparc.c, * elfxx-tilegx.c, * elfxx-x86.c,
	* reloc.c: Replace use of %R and %T in format strings passed to
	einfo and friends by %pR and %pT.

